title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 11 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 11 2022
description:
Shifting narrative: Trump's power move has FBI/DOJ on defense. Clay says, "Trump is, for all of the criticisms that people out there levy against him, innately aware of advantage and leverage... When you have leverage on your side, you exploit it." Why did the FBI spend 9 hours searching Mar-a-Lago? Demand answers, but don't let Christopher Wray January 6th us. Raid blunder could clear the GOP primary field for Trump. Buck says, "This is very directly tied to the fact that, with more information here, this does seem to be a fishing expedition, a massive overreach, and a blunder."

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
